{"tid":425944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[請人]網上銷售員","createTime":"2017-10-06T07:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T11:24:48.000Z","uid":152029,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"325eb2b7da8fa3599d0dc9f74a7aeab7ea9ec11f","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次誠意請人，公司係PCCW 網上銷售部門，部門只有十個人，工作地點係葵興KC100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依份工我個人認為適合咁多位連登巴打，原因為下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先工作範圍係網上開post或者pm（討論區,FACEBOOK等等），每日番7個鐘（3PM-10PM）仲有1個鐘放飯，唔洗輪班輪休（固定星期日休息），最好係唔洗日曬雨淋擺街（全程寫字樓上班 無須外出），同事都係廿零歲大家都有傾有講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁當然模式有別於面對面客既SALES<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢份工勤力係需要但變通更緊要。份工係網上搵客傾Plan，呢個模式未必個個都適應（但可以入黎試試 有專人指導）。番夜晚可能大家都有唔同睇法，有巴打會覺得唔洗咁早起身係優點，亦有巴打覺得番夜好難約朋友食飯（不過工時唔長又有禮拜日放，呢方面要就番其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n底薪＋佣平均每月有＄15000－25000（底薪＄6000），有同事做到平均＄60000以上（佢係最top）。一年有12日大假，有醫療卡福利，做夠2年有約滿酬金，無需經驗（岩岩畢業都可以試下），中五學歷同夠18歲就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩直接搵我都可以解答各位巴打（WTS/CALL: 53774797）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者有問題可以留言我會盡力回覆所有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e53f0de164cd5412590f5f15a8158bd4756915","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"808c73e28f08adf465a3025ff7f07727480ef808","tid":425944,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:38:10.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"b8cf4acffd16f40c75d74ffa874e607f97cd6e91","tid":425944,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7faa029538ba82554aa284a31e5bb401dd2698","tid":425944,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"60k個d係打手<br />\n同online game排名一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16022ff1038a400a0cdeed76dfdfe6cc090a053a","tid":425944,"uid":140434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"底薪6千? 每週工時5*7?"},{"pid":"57988ebca95e726c0c317ac1b80218f2cc4a4113","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>底薪6千? 每週工時5*7?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地部門同擺街計法一樣<br />\n每張單既佣金比例高 例如會有單錢既8%-10% 所以一張上網會有$500<br />\n<br />\n一張sim 卡會有$800"},{"pid":"8d960738c5ba48ad7a0f406949fce9b0e6f05618","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打幫推"},{"pid":"edc712544c904b61f6186782904ec4c56a81316e","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公司垃唔垃圾我唔方便評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係打工都係睇錢呀自問搵到食同工作環境對比其他sales我認為不錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f83b4bcba2913a3eb57b22351c670670f94f012","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"覆"},{"pid":"ee0a297b666f4f202350e714026da7ad5340d4f5","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T18:59:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9381afd6b4c1c06102cede235082ae30b7c3b48","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"178292caca8e0df63401cfca594f911082608345","tid":425944,"uid":9853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"多唔多女女做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3063fa30b1884338662d2a4615a98ba1150fa9","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多唔多女女做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部門而家八個人 有三個係女女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3160553ba97f16667e3f45d7c92f08ac8cdbaeeb","tid":425944,"uid":114504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"老電唔係14日annual咩，仲有兩日去左邊？"},{"pid":"d29bf1b2462a2aa67b0f98a9cf9cdec6d338b258","tid":425944,"uid":9853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多唔多女女做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部門而家八個人 有三個係女女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無圖睇睇"},{"pid":"30fb0ebc21d7c61393aa0f3bfe74b96118fb8634","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多唔多女女做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部門而家八個人 有三個係女女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無圖睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nnow tv 官網有圖"},{"pid":"6548a65b71032a65640be551bed045d1ed8c0e6a","tid":425944,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid